  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "画期的なパチンコゲーム「パチ夫くん」の続編です。前作から店舗数が10に増加しました。コングテーブルやUFOテーブルなど、ユニークなパチンコ台の種類も増えました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The second NES Pachio-kun game, about a sentient pachinko ball that loves playing pachinko. It was published by Coconuts Japan.\n\nPachiokun 2 is the sequel to Pachiokun, and was also published by slot machine manufacturer Coconuts Japan as well as developed by contract developers Marionette and C Dream. As with the first game, the goal is to help a sentient pachinko ball named Pachio-kun bankrupt a series of pachinko parlors and liberate all his miniature brethren from their flashy mechanical gulags.\n\nThe game introduces Pachio-kun's wife, presumably named Pachio-chan. If she's upset about her husband's gambling addiction, she never shows it.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
